{
  "stem": "14867.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "So-- and so-- and then, of course, with the winter, it was closed.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And we were all sitting.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And there was a small sukkah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "But I still remember, we were all sitting along this long table.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "It was very informal, very, like, rustic.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And the-- the windows of the kitchen were looking out to the backyard.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there you had-- we had to have the stable, because my father would always come with three horses home.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "So you had a stable for the horses, and you had for-- we had a cow, one cow there, that gave us always milk.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And then we had, in the backyard, a big like a-- a bungalow.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And there were no refrigerators, but the whole floor had blocks of ice.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "So a lot of our neighbors would come and keep their-- their food there, especially for the holiday.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 54,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "They would-- they would buy a lot of stuff, and they didn't have any-- any ice.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I will always remember they would come and ask for permission.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother said, you don't have to ask permission.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You just go and put it in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So another way in-- in the house had two big gates, the-- the yard, the front yard.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So one was for the horses to come in, and the other side was to come out.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And-- and my mother-- my maternal grandmother lived with-- in downstairs in our house.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So-- and she had a-- a-- a daughter who was not married.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So she was always sitting in front of the gate, right inside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And a passerby would at least stop and chat with her, because she was in a wheelchair and couldn't walk around.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "My mother spent every day some time with her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we also had a-- a big, big foyer.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
